              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Natural copper targets that have two odd-mass",
                "isotopes of abundances 63Cu(68.17%) and 65Cu(30.83%)",
                "The excitation functions were measured in three steps",
                "namely 50-20 MeV, 40-10 MeV and 30-10 MeV, using copper",
                "foils of thicknesses 23 mg/cm2, 8.9 mg/cm2 and",
                "12 mg/cm2, respectively, together with several",
                "aluminium degraders of varying thicknesses to reduce",
                "the beam energy to desired levels."
              ]
            }
